@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Message Flow Detail

participant Producer
participant Kafka
participant Topic
participant Partition
participant Consumer

Producer -> Kafka: Produce(message, topic="demo-topic")
Kafka -> Topic: Route to Topic
Topic -> Partition: Assign to Partition
Partition -> Partition: Append Message
Partition --> Kafka: Acknowledge (offset)
Kafka --> Producer: Success (offset)

note right of Consumer: Consumer polls for messages
Consumer -> Kafka: Fetch from topic (from last offset)
Kafka -> Topic: Get messages
Topic -> Partition: Read from Partition
Partition --> Topic: Return messages
Topic --> Kafka: Messages with offsets
Kafka --> Consumer: Deliver messages

Consumer -> Consumer: Process eachMessage()
Consumer -> Kafka: Commit offset
Kafka -> Partition: Update consumer offset

@enduml

